Question: Both images show exteriors, and the left image shows a primitive yurt-type structure with no windows and with gray material around it, while the right shows a structure with a black cap on its peak.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/f0/f7/6b/f0f76b300ce268616621a772deb10aa0.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.ebayimg.com/00/s/NzY4WDEwMjQ=/z/lS8AAOSwGJlZIzy3/$_86.JPG

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the image an exterior?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the image an exterior?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the image a primitive yurt-type structure with no windows and with gray material around it?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the image a structure with a black cap on its peak?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
